INSERT INTO dspfirst (id,meta,name,content,chapter,section,paragraph) VALUES(6856,'paragraph',NULL,'\iffalse %&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; <div class="ITS_EXE"><div class="ITS_EXE_logo">Exercise:</div> Show by drawing pictures like Fig. <a href="fig:eval_conv" class="ITS_reference">&raquo;</a>(a) for finite-duration signals of arbitrary shape that if <span class="ITS_HTML">x(t)=0</span> for <span class="ITS_HTML">t<T<sub>0</sub></span> and <span class="ITS_HTML">t>T<sub>2</sub></span> and <span class="ITS_HTML">h(t)=0</span> for <span class="ITS_HTML">t<T<sub>1</sub></span> and <span class="ITS_HTML">t>T<sub>3</sub></span>, then the output <span class="ITS_HTML">y(t)=x(t)*h(t)=0</span> for <span class="ITS_HTML">t<T<sub>0</sub>+T<sub>1</sub></span> and <span class="ITS_HTML">t>T<sub>2</sub>+T<sub>3</sub></span>. </div> \fi %&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;','9','8','11');
